      "text": "                 User uploads video to s3 \n                                  |\n                   video Processing Pipeline \n\nffmpeg converts the video into segments(seg1, seg2, seg3, ....)                                                          \n                                   |\nThese segments are transcoded(Transcoding = converting video from one encoding/quality to another.) ",
      "fontSize": 62.17766890381561,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "                 User uploads video to s3 \n                                  |\n                   video Processing Pipeline \n\nffmpeg converts the video into segments(seg1, seg2, seg3, ....)                                                          \n                                   |\nThese segments are transcoded(Transcoding = converting video from one encoding/quality to another.) ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
