    {
      "id": "TTsm80Sy0ZKlVOg__l6B-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3590.760801749149,
      "y": 33603.28437317761,
      "width": 4494.236511678974,
      "height": 267.0449205820732,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2w",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1097631665,
      "version": 335,
      "versionNonce": 808770257,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783340994021,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Uploads are write-heavy, but video platforms are overwhelmingly read-heavy (watch-heavy), \nso the biggest scaling wins come from caching metadata and serving video segments through CDNs.",
      "fontSize": 98.9055261415086,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Uploads are write-heavy, but video platforms are overwhelmingly read-heavy (watch-heavy), \nso the biggest scaling wins come from caching metadata and serving video segments through CDNs.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "bplOGacX4QL6QrOw-S6EU",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2954.6601004589334,
      "y": 27386.548452869574,
      "width": 871.2255859375,
      "height": 332.08249622087783,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b30",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1005417727,
      "version": 45,
      "versionNonce": 2059754239,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783334697886,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Redis Cache\nKey = video:<videoId>\nValue = VideoMetadata",
      "fontSize": 81.9956780792291,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Redis Cache\nKey = video:<videoId>\nValue = VideoMetadata",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "8DYpnNbn99OulMBKxon0t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1184.8190274852832,
      "y": 27382.35781790337,
      "width": 1521.1380615234375,
      "height": 1174.853231880348,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b31",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1515012625,
      "version": 111,
      "versionNonce": 1458225329,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783334816990,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What is cached?\n\nUsually the frequently-read metadata:\n\nvideo:123\n    ↓\nmetadat: \n    - name\n    - description\n    - user\n    - s3 Url's\n\nNot the actual video segments.\n\nThe video segments are served from S3 + CDN, not Redis.",
      "fontSize": 58.01744354964681,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "What is cached?\n\nUsually the frequently-read metadata:\n\nvideo:123\n    ↓\nmetadat: \n    - name\n    - description\n    - user\n    - s3 Url's\n\nNot the actual video segments.\n\nThe video segments are served from S3 + CDN, not Redis.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "f9wIAiIHbwdBlqo6GRMM3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2996.45760795181,
      "y": 27955.052090993344,
      "width": 1213.7574242936732,
      "height": 540.88564542315,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b32",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 117465137,
      "version": 69,
      "versionNonce": 1960135807,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783334860937,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "VideoMetadata in Cassandra:\n{\n  \"videoId\": \"123\",\n  \"title\": \"Funny Cat Video\",\n  \"manifestUrl\": \"s3://videos/123/master.m3u8\",\n  \"creatorId\": \"u456\"\n}",
      "fontSize": 57.23657623525398,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "VideoMetadata in Cassandra:\n{\n  \"videoId\": \"123\",\n  \"title\": \"Funny Cat Video\",\n  \"manifestUrl\": \"s3://videos/123/master.m3u8\",\n  \"creatorId\": \"u456\"\n}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "J9xe4SRD7VfpkxNAzuPcd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2961.3530791471385,
      "y": 28636.223370796226,
      "width": 1355.4697265625,
      "height": 658.0238971031096,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b33",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1597472369,
      "version": 159,
      "versionNonce": 999682431,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783334917590,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Redis:\nKey: video:123\nValue:\n    {\n      \"title\": \"Funny Cat Video\",\n      \"manifestUrl\": \"s3://videos/123/master.m3u8\",\n      \"userId\": \"u456\"\n    }",
      "fontSize": 60.92813862065829,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Redis:\nKey: video:123\nValue:\n    {\n      \"title\": \"Funny Cat Video\",\n      \"manifestUrl\": \"s3://videos/123/master.m3u8\",\n      \"userId\": \"u456\"\n    }",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "sgtbb7uFh09pcnJCv1Lu9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 854.5192850694266,
      "y": 27396.12478801187,
      "width": 616.0559692382812,
      "height": 1238.232176632302,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b34",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2131896689,
      "version": 195,
      "versionNonce": 1610631825,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783334982028,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Read Flow\nGET /videos/123\n       ↓\nRedis GET video:123\n\nIf found:\n    Return metadata\n\nIf not found:\n    Read Cassandra\n          ↓\n    SET video:123\n          ↓\n    Return metadata",
      "fontSize": 65.51492998054508,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Read Flow\nGET /videos/123\n       ↓\nRedis GET video:123\n\nIf found:\n    Return metadata\n\nIf not found:\n    Read Cassandra\n          ↓\n    SET video:123\n          ↓\n    Return metadata",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "L1ev4ohCu8Bnd401nE0kT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3575.1076975157584,
      "y": 34373.046399170344,
      "width": 1722.0220947265625,
      "height": 134.88067537260585,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b35",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1521252657,
      "version": 219,
      "versionNonce": 2000584703,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783337163912,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CDN(Content-Delivery-Network):",
      "fontSize": 117.28754380226597,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CDN(Content-Delivery-Network):",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "LMhL4mZ7l1y5wB8c69ECp",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3393.960584111369,
      "y": 34571.93579048386,
      "width": 5272.47216796875,
      "height": 624.6001393242834,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b36",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 229965457,
      "version": 231,
      "versionNonce": 1480075871,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783337311227,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "-  a globally distributed group of servers that temporarily stores (or caches) website content near end users\n- drastically reduces page load times and bandwith consumption.\n\n- Instead of sending every user request across the world to a single main server (the origin server), a CDN relies on \"Points of Presence\" (PoPs).\n- When a user requests a web page, image, or video, the CDN intercepts the request and routes it to the nearest PoP, serving the cached content locally\n-  If the content isn't cached, the PoP retrieves it from the origin server, caches a copy for the next user, and passes it on.",
      "fontSize": 77.11112831163993,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "-  a globally distributed group of servers that temporarily stores (or caches) website content near end users\n- drastically reduces page load times and bandwith consumption.\n\n- Instead of sending every user request across the world to a single main server (the origin server), a CDN relies on \"Points of Presence\" (PoPs).\n- When a user requests a web page, image, or video, the CDN intercepts the request and routes it to the nearest PoP, serving the cached content locally\n-  If the content isn't cached, the PoP retrieves it from the origin server, caches a copy for the next user, and passes it on.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
